OptionButton Flags
#include Style
#Background wimp 1
Gadget:	<OptionButton=>Optionbox>
#Line
#Wrap off
Bits:	0	- Set means generate an <OptionButton_StateChanged=>OptionButton_StateChanged> when user clicks.
	2	- Set means that the Option Button is on when first created.

Constants:
	<OptionButton_StateChanged_Adjust>
	<OptionButton_StateChanged_Select>
#Line
To be used with <Gadget_Set_Flags=>Gadget_Set_Flags>
